  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Our children and youth have lost 5,120 hours of class due to the hurricanes, earthquakes and pandemic Puerto Rico has endured in the past three years. Living in vulnerable communities, BGCPR participants are experiencing more inequalities than ever. To bridge the gap, we are providing virtual academic and socioemotional support, meals and free internet access. A small donation now will bring the certainty of better futures and will help them succeed over time.</narrative>
  </description>
